__e: Unless Gaius Julius Caesar immediately lays down his command, disbands his legions and returns to Rome for trial, this sacred assembly will declare him a public enemy of the Senate and people of Rome!
On this eve of his most glorious triumph, I move that Gaius Julius Caesar be made Imperator and granted absolute power over Rome for a period of ten years.
As of this day, the Kalends of February, our beloved father dictator... Gaius Julius Caesar has decreed that 100 new men be raised to the Senate of the Republic.
